Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.34,0:00:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《边桥谜案》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Previously on The Bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是杰克·多布斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Jack Dobbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来探视的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, so, you here to see someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探视你哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是桑娅·克罗斯  丽莎的妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Sonya Cross, Lisa's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你到底在找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我现在还不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我看到了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边到底怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's going on down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  有人想要杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yesterday someone tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确定那是我们自己人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was one of my own men.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来美国做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you plan to do in the U.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美国前往墨西哥华瑞兹市\N请出示护照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美国前往墨西哥华瑞兹市\N请出示护照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女汉子出马了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了  哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm out of here, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好冷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的衣服哪去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened to your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有人血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There was man blood on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们该报警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe we should call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道恩典吗  凯尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you known grace, Kyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩典\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞穿万物的圣光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The light that goes through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的已经耗尽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've used up all of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许对你来说还不算晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe it's not too late for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, okay, okay, okay, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你摸我下面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I will let you touch me down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不穿粉色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't wear pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我再回去  他们会醒来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, they'll wake up if I go back in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会倒霉的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It would be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没穿过粉色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've never worn pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是给妓女还有想当公主的小女孩穿的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's for whores and little girls who want to be princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找别的衣服  拜托了  凯尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something else. Please, Kyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫什么名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没看到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣光从他身上褪去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The light coming off him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We should go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该跟他道别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You should say good-bye to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:07:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}边桥谜案  第二季第二集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖狗狗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颈动脉被割开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tore the carotid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不像刀伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doesn't look like a knife wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正效果不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did the job though, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不用刀子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why not a knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该随手抓起什么吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Used what was handy, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So unplanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自卫吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧  也可能不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么车没熄火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why keep the car running?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是需要一段时间让他的血流干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Took a while for him to bleed out, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  这种油电混合车  很难说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Plus, these electric jobs, you can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这整件事要是有一点符合常理就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Be nice if something about this whole thing made sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车里好像还坐了一个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think there was a woman in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你请假了对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You took a personal day yesterday, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有32天假没用呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have 32 unused personal days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看多布斯了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you go see Dobbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  我没去看他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nope, I didn't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多布斯的弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dobbs's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我们一起吃午饭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, we had lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给了他一张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I gave him a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们  一起  聊天了  他人很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We... just... talked. He's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们聊什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What'd you talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们聊丽莎了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We talked about Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的哥哥杀了你姐姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That man's brother killed your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不能说明他是罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That doesn't make him a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从统计学上来说  没理由假定他也是罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Statistically speaking, there's no reason to assume that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扯淡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是个男人你会这样跟我说话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you be talking to me like this if I was a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不会  -这就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是专心工作吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So why don't we just work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是埃尔帕索警局的桑娅·克罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sonya Cross, El Paso PD.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉他们我不干那种事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I told them I don't do that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想打电话报警...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I was gonna call you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你做什么  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Make you do what, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是为地下室里那东西来的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I assume you're here about what's in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一个月前来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They, uh, came in about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚是怎么知道我名字和电话的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Didn't-didn't say where they got my name or number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说有活让我干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just said they had a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是两个人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There were two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  一个男人  一个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, yeah, the... uh... um, a man and a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And this woman, she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来有点古怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14} she was kind of peculiar, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他们名字吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get their names?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  我没问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, ma'am. I-I didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉  但我跟他们说得很明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm-I'm sorry. I'm sorry, but i-I was very clear with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想接这份工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I told them I did not want this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人威胁说要砍掉我的双手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The partner, he said he was going to cut off my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀光我全家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and kill my entire family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上  他们付的是现金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Plus, they-they paid cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, it's-it's... it's right in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Luisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}起床  我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}再睡会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我得去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不用付了  警探
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}奇瓦瓦州警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}他被吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你丢东西了还是怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}很牛是吗  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你觉得自己很牛是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}是不是想毙了我  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}拿着  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}赶紧拿着  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个没种的孬货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Marco,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那些血迹洗不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我们约好了的  记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:14:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我们待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个标本师说子弹是从狗身上取出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Taxidermist said he took this bullet out of the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那尸体呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指纹估计都被虫子吃光了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, the beetles pretty well took care of the prints,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能去查牙医记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so we'll submit dental records.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔  有什么可以效劳的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Joe, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的狗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's our dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扬基\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yankee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在警方通报的犯罪现场资料中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The dog was mentioned in a crime scene
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们注意到了这只狗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}flyer your department circulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正指望你们能帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we were hoping for help identifying the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定车里死者的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}John Doe in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要看这件案子的详细档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna need to see the complete file,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有材料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}everything you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我为什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want to tell me why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看过档案才能确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Won't know until i've seen the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是一男一女  就像我刚刚说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was a man and a woman and, like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前从来没见过他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never saw either 'em before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  女士  就是他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, yes, yes, ma'am, that was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人什么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她像是他的老板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, she was... she was like the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着个特别大的账簿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She had this big ledger book,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四处走动  看到什么都要记下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and she went around taking notes about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的着装挺搞笑的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And she dressed kind of funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像虔诚的教徒或阿米什人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, churchy, or Amishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车里没发现毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, no dope in the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标本师那里也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}no dope at the taxidermist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道缉毒局会对标本狗感兴趣吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the DEA taking an interest in stuffed dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在感兴趣了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在标本师那里发现的死者叫吉米·泰卡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The John Doe you found at the taxidermist is Jimmy Tecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的卧底探员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Undercover field agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那狗也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The dog, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节哀顺变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但案子是我们发现的  就是我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}However, we caught the case. It's ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  现在不是了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说这尸体的事了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They say anything about the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不太高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Um, they weren't too happy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我说需要用槌打它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when I said I needed to beetle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想把人尸做成标本吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They wanted it mounted?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  要摆好姿势  可是尸体腐烂得太厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Posed, yes, ma'am, but it was too far gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布满蛆虫  还要放尸气  而且...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maggots and off gassing, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更别说这事完全是犯法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not to mention the illegality of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但问题是  他们把尸体放在了储存袋里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, but the problem was, they had it in a storage unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种温度下放置了两天  我也无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Two days in this heat, there ain't nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缉毒局的人来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The DEA's outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃奶糖不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法国生产的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中间是海盐夹心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They got this sea salt in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这糖对牙齿不好  不过我特别喜欢吃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're hell on the crowns, but I like 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不吃糖  -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I don't do sugar. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有害健康\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如这样  我们何不都坐下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}tell you what. Why don't we sit down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个执法人员的样子  都专业些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I'll tell you what I got, you tell me what you got,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好谈谈  互相交换下情报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and we act like law enforcement professionals?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真挺好吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  再来一块吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, here. Have another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首席调查员桑娅·克罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lead investigator Sonya Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑娅  这是缉毒局的乔·麦肯齐和皮特·里瓦斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sonya, this is Joe McKenzie and Pete Rivas from the DEA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门带上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颈动脉多处刺伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Multiple stab wounds to the carotid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘客逃离了现场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Passenger fled the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤凡尼·加尔萨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yovani Garza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是福斯托·加尔文的保镖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's an escort for Fausto Galvan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车上没有毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There were no drugs in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我们已经谈过了  桑娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've been over that, Sonya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有乘客特征描述吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You get a description of the passenger?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性  黑发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, female, brunette.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标本师说她身上带着什么总账\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Taxidermist said she has some sort of ledger with her;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为她是管事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}thought that she was in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起什么来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does that ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是女朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could be a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会查的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那泰卡探员呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about Agent Tecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰卡探员和扬基在华瑞兹帮我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Agent Tecca and Yankee were responsible for
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缴获超过三顿毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}over three tons of seizures,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕了无数罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}dozens of arrests in Juarez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们沉重打击了福斯托·加尔文的生意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They put a serious dent in Fausto Galvan's operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他什么时候失踪的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When did he go missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑犯要把泰卡探员制成标本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our suspects wanted Agent Tecca mounted,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但腐烂太严重了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the decomp was too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人都变态的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}These people are depraved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们不要提到剥制过程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'd prefer you leave out mention of the taxidermy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这种事会给家属造成伤害的  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Something like that can hurt the family. - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲自训练的泰卡探员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I personally trained Agent Tecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起打保龄球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're on the same bowling team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你们准备怎么划分职责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, um, so how do you want to chop this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰卡是我们的人  案子由我们负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Since Tecca was ours, we'll take the lead on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我们负责查加尔萨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good, good. We'll take Garza.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副驾驶上的人呢  那个女的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about the passenger-- the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个也由我们负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, we'll want to be in on that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做任何事之前  请先跟我们协调一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just don't make any moves without coordinating with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗要给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I want the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  狗是这案子的证物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I'm sorry, the dog is evidence in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这狗是他妈的英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The dog is a goddamn hero;
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让它坐在证物室里积灰尘的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not gonna have it sitting in some evidence room gathering dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这不合规...  -可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That is against pro... - You got a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你带了一个三明治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Brought you a PBJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理掉了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are they gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is it safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了巴士  把东西丢下了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got on the bus and ditched,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你说的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just like you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在想摸我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you want to touch me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会开车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚拿到学习驾照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just have my learner's permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是会开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但必须有成人陪同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only with an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是个成年人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-到吃药的时间了吗  -还没\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Time for your daily two? - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's that going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三小时之后会好很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go a lot better three hours from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那副表情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't give me that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:21:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hola, buenos tardes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头一个小时300比索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}300 pesos for the first hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后每小时180比索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}180 pesos for each additional hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先付钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pay in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  厕所没有纸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we out of towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不是的  我们是来找劳尔·昆塔纳的\N他在这家酒吧工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我们能进去找找看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}随你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来两杯可乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can I get two Cokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来点威士忌吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure you don't want to throw some whiskey in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是工作时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're working.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我都忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, yeah, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯着别人看是很不礼貌的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, it's rude to stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本停不下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How can you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如此高大  又如此美丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's six-foot-four and gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的本能被召唤出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm finding myself genuinely aroused.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你好  我们在找劳尔·昆塔纳\N你认识他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.30,0:23:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳尔·昆塔纳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Raul Quintana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not saying it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博尼托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bonito.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳尔·昆塔纳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Raul Quintana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的神啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ay, chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是太太太性感了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you are... like, that was muy, muy, muy es caliente.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想问你几个问题  关于你的阿姨米莉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We want to ask you some questions about your aunt Millie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么找到我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你房东告诉我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁派你们来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是埃尔帕索时报的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're with the El Paso Times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是想问几个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We just want to ask you some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你阿姨死后一周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, look, uh, a week after your aunt died,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的亲属便被驱逐出境了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you and your relatives were deported.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  我是时报的记者丹尼尔·弗莱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What... uh, look, Daniel Frye. The Times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:24:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们六个月前已经获准避难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Six months after getting asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是狗屎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This doesn't mean shit to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道你们不是条子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do I know you're not cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  我可不是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, trust me, I'm not a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.66,0:24:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们驱逐你的时候有说理由吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did they give you a reason when they deported you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.31,0:24:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别  请你别走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whoa, whoa. No, no, please don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.17,0:24:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都可以跟我们说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, anything you can tell us, at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.57,0:24:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如那六千万  比如你阿姨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about the 60 million bucks, and your aunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.57,0:24:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可以说说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that'd be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.31,0:24:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只想知道你阿姨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We just want to know how your aunt
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么和贩毒集团搞上的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}got mixed up with the cartel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贩毒集团\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cartel?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.77,0:24:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么好说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not talking about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们离开这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.68,0:24:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄  淡定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, chillax, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.70,0:24:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.29,0:24:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  丹尼尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, my God, Daniel...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.15,0:24:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.21,0:24:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.41,0:24:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起钓鱼的海关署朋友一小时前给的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A fishing buddy at ICE got me this an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.43,0:24:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉克看过了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hank seen this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.49,0:24:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缉毒局也同时要了这段监控录像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The DEA requested the same footage, same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.67,0:25:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者就是他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's your dead guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.12,0:25:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.97,0:25:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.90,0:25:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.95,0:25:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得她信教吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you call that "Churchy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.56,0:25:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得她特别虔诚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd call that downright devout.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.60,0:25:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打印出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Print it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.49,0:25:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全面通缉她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Put out an APB.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.95,0:25:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让汉克看  不告诉缉毒局吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Run it by Hank? Loop in the DEA?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.82,0:25:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们去调取海关署录像也没告诉我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They didn't inform us they pulled the ICE tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.24,0:25:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发布通缉令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Put it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.87,0:25:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.71,0:26:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不是说好一个小时后见面的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.45,0:26:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}没错  但现在不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.06,0:26:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我来一杯威士忌苏打\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eh, un whiskey soda, por favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.85,0:26:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gracias.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.99,0:26:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}今天发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.63,0:26:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你是想在这里审问我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.30,0:26:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不是  就是聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.12,0:26:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.71,0:26:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你不相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.50,0:26:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.06,0:26:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你今天这招很妙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.02,0:26:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}非常妙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.70,0:26:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你这发生了很多事\N所有人都知道该注意谁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.83,0:26:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}他们把你从墨西哥派来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.42,0:26:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}让我们以为你真的关心华瑞兹
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.31,0:26:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}所以你就抓了几个警察
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.57,0:27:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}把他们扔进监狱关了一周\N以为事情就解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.64,0:27:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}没有什么真相\N马可
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.49,0:27:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}只有不同版本的真相...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.40,0:27:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}够了  别说废话了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.81,0:27:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你想知道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.54,0:27:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mira.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.79,0:27:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}雨果·马科斯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.34,0:27:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}在索尔街信号灯下被枪杀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.08,0:27:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}被杀两小时前  你和他有过争执
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.91,0:27:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Si, him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.42,0:27:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}关于什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.10,0:27:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你想知道的就是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.35,0:27:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}这可以很大程度上帮助我了解这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.50,0:27:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}他跟我说了一些不该说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.82,0:27:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}比如
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.73,0:27:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你知道有人说怎么你们警局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.52,0:27:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}年轻女人来到警局求助
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.22,0:28:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}而她们却再也没有出来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.50,0:28:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你正在踏入一条非常危险的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.87,0:28:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你确定你要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.99,0:28:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我那是一袋子满满的纯氧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please tell me that's a bag full of Oxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.09,0:28:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你买的阿司匹林\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got you aspirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.19,0:28:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿司匹林没用的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Aspirin's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.43,0:28:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人问起我的伤口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, if anyone ever asks,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.35,0:28:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说我是在飙车族酒吧为了保护你弄的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I did this defending your honor at a biker bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.95,0:28:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  随你便\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.21,0:28:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼尔  你害我们把这事搞砸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You really screwed us on this, daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.91,0:28:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.34,0:28:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.94,0:28:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来  喂  喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.64,0:28:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.19,0:28:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  亲爱的  我刚刚是不得已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry, honey, I had to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.17,0:28:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打疼了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.38,0:28:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.94,0:28:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想被人看见我跟你说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't want to be seen talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.03,0:29:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我阿姨死后发生了很多稀奇诡异的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Weird shit has been happening since my aunt died.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.86,0:29:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在跟踪你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is someone following you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.25,0:29:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.78,0:29:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.78,0:29:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.66,0:29:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么有人要跟踪你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why would somebody want to be following you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.14,0:29:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找的人叫楚奇托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The person you want to talk to is Chuchito.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.77,0:29:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他帮我阿姨筹了钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He helped my aunt with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.02,0:29:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么筹的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In what kind of way?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.67,0:29:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你得问他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have to ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.97,0:29:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是朋友吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Were you guys friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.48,0:29:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.50,0:29:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我很担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm-I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.22,0:29:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经一周没见到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Haven't seen him in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.21,0:29:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢去他住处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm afraid to go by his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.73,0:29:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.81,0:29:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了啊  我被人盯上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm telling you, i'm being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  放松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.29,0:29:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们找到他  叫他给他亲爱的回个电\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you find him, can you tell him to call his bomboncito?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.06,0:29:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我懂了  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Oh, I get it. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.54,0:29:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他发生了些事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.64,0:29:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.63,0:29:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.06,0:29:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我有事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You wanted something?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.61,0:29:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  进来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yep. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.78,0:29:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门关上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.29,0:30:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没告诉我你让库珀调取了海关署的监控视频\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't tell me that you had Cooper pull that ICE video.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.40,0:30:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有图片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got an image.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.27,0:30:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就直接对这个女人下了全面通缉令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you went ahead and put out an APB on this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.75,0:30:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.34,0:30:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑娅  你当时在场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were here, Sonya.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.30,0:30:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也听到我们对那些人的承诺了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You heard what we had agreed to with those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.72,0:30:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这些事情上应该提前跟他们打招呼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We owe them a heads-up on something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.24,0:30:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得在她回墨西哥之前找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to find her before she goes back to Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.30,0:30:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们希望你按规矩办事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need for you to follow protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.08,0:30:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没和我们共享移民局的录像带\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They didn't share the ICE tapes with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.23,0:30:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑娅  这样很容易激怒他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sonya, something like this is liable to set them off.
