Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.71,0:42:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}尤凡尼在为我护送一件重要包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.92,0:42:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}一个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.99,0:42:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我要你找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.19,0:42:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}赶在美国人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.26,0:42:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}如果我拒绝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.49,0:42:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}加尔文先生  这个人优柔寡断
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.05,0:42:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我相信马可会做出正确的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.98,0:42:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}鉴于我们的事业当前面临的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.87,0:42:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我建议你采取更谨慎的措施
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.74,0:42:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}更适合做这件事的人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.12,0:42:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}他们很乐意为自己的忠诚而获得表彰
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.30,0:42:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我们是一诺千金之人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.31,0:43:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不是吗  马可
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.49,0:43:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手指怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened to your finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.81,0:43:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在换浴缸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm replacing the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.93,0:43:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陶瓷质量差\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The tiles are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.85,0:43:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道怎么换吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know how to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.49,0:43:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.84,0:43:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mm, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.85,0:43:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能进去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.19,0:44:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.93,0:44:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要喝杯水吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you like a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.82,0:44:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, sure. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.70,0:44:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天的事我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.81,0:44:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大老远跑过来道歉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You came all this way to apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.60,0:44:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mm, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.48,0:44:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不全是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.04,0:44:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在办尤凡尼·加尔萨的案子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yovani Garza case, you have it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.20,0:44:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.74,0:44:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缉毒局也介入了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}DEA is involved, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.19,0:44:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.79,0:44:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那情况就不同了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That changes things.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.65,0:44:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's one of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.85,0:45:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥籍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A Mexican national.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.33,0:45:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是贩毒集团的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's cartel.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.88,0:45:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.28,0:45:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伯斯队长派我过来办这个案子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Captain Robles sent me here to work the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.59,0:45:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.66,0:45:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他派你来监视我们这些美国佬吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's sending you to keep an eye on the Americans?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.48,0:45:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  差不多这个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.00,0:45:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴这个人是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I'm glad it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.43,0:45:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.75,0:45:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看看你都有什么线索吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can I see what you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.86,0:45:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.77,0:45:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.11,0:45:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不太专业啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not a professional job, you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.58,0:45:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车里还有谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who else was in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.31,0:45:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和一个女人起了争执\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He crossed with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.38,0:45:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得有点奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kind of strange-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.49,0:45:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.34,0:46:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认得她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you recognize her?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.97,0:46:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.51,0:46:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.72,0:46:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看你都查到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So show me everything you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.42,0:46:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那个在公园见到我的朋友...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your friend who saw me in the park...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.14,0:46:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说德克西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You mean Dex?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.82,0:46:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德克西  他住哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dex. Where does he live?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.70,0:46:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.84,0:46:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.22,0:46:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道他住哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to know where he lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.53,0:46:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯勒街\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.27,0:46:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是栋前面有篱笆的绿房子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's the green house with a hoop in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.95,0:46:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地址呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Address?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.54,0:46:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.83,0:46:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了  是绿房子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like I said, it's green.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.07,0:46:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能问你个问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.38,0:46:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.80,0:46:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么纹了这么多纹身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why do you have all those tattoos?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.36,0:47:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来纪念我认识的恶魔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They are marks to remember the demons I've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.71,0:47:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.17,0:47:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的恶魔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not real demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.99,0:47:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真酷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.00,0:47:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么味道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.80,0:47:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只浣熊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A raccoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.09,0:47:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬进来死掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It crawled in here and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.13,0:47:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.52,0:47:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私密的分享就应该保密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's shared in private should be kept private.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.67,0:47:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.89,0:47:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.18,0:47:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟女人上过床吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you been with a woman before?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.58,0:47:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.22,0:48:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想摸摸吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you like to touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.98,0:48:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.17,0:48:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.42,0:48:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都看不见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.71,0:48:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.57,0:48:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终将有光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The light will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.92,0:48:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照彻你身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It will pass through you.

